title: This is What I Call Minimal 80s! Vol. 8
description:
And here it is, Vol. 8 of these minimal synth mixes. Hope you'll like it. This is dedicated to my pal, Edward, whom I was fortunate enough to know from the pirate bay, wishing him the best in the new adventure of his life.
